My PM Routine 💕
⁃  Pink Cloud Cleanser: a super gentle cleanser that takes off all my makeup while leaving my skin feeling clean and hydrated. I love to steam after cleansing to help open up my pores
⁃  Bakuchiol Serum: targets signs of fine lines, helps with texture and any sort of dullness to help maintain my youthful glow
⁃  Lapis Face Oil: This is amazing for acne-prone skin! I like to incorporate this around ‘that time of the month’ to prevent any crazy bumps from popping up.
⁃  Jade Roller: Helps to reduce puffiness *tip* I store this in my fridge for a cooling effect that helps de-puff my skin.
⁃  Rose Hibiscus Hydrating Facial Mist: I live for drenching my face in this amazing mist. It has amazing ingredients like Rose, Aloe, + Coconut water to hydrate and soothe my skin.

Ready to meet the cream you’ve been dreaming of? 💭NEW today! 

PINK CLOUD Soft Moisture Cream, made with: 
💕Tremella mushroom, a humectant that draws water from the air to the skin (and outperforms topical hyaluronic acid!) 
☁️ Vegan squalane, an oil that creates a shield over the skin to lock in moisture 
💕Aloe to help retain moisture and sodium hyaluronate to draw water deep into skin 
☁️ The blend of humectant + oil creates a super-hydrating moisturizer that supports a healthy skin barrier so skin stays soft, smooth, and looks plump 

AQUARIUS Pore Purifying Clarity Cream, made with: 
♒ White willow bark BHA, a naturally-sourced salicylic acid that goes deep into pores to help clear out congestion and build-up 
💦Blue tansy oil, an ingredient that helps balance oily skin 
♒ Magnesium PCA a humectant that draws water to your skin and witch hazel a gentle astringent that helps clean pores
💦The blend of clarifying + soothing ingredients helps balance hydration levels and keeps pores clear, so freakout-prone skin looks calmer and more refined 

Need help choosing? Hit us with your Qs in the comments and we'll help you find your dream cream. 

#HerbivoreDreamCreams
